<text>
    <body>
        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Lead deliveries, August 8, 14, 26, 28, September 5, 20, 1817. Elias Bates's receipts to Stephen F. Austin.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Herculmn</placeName>. <date when="1817-08-08">Augs 8th 1817</date></p>
<p>Sir</p>
<p><persName>Mr J Staples</persName> delivd 81 Bars of lead weighing 3352 lb</p>
<p><persName>Elias Bates</persName></p>
<p><persName>Mr S F Austin</persName></p>

<p><persName>Mr S F Austin</persName></p>
<p><persName>Mr John Staples</persName> Delivd 71 Bars of Lead weighing Twenty Nine
Hundred and twelve pounds.</p>
<p>71 Brs 2912 lb   <date when="1817-08-14">Augst 14th 1817</date></p>
<p><persName>Elias Bates</persName></p>

<p><persName>Mr S F Austin</persName></p>
<p><persName>Mr John Staples</persName> delivd&#8212;40 1/2 Bars of lead weighing&#8212;sixteen 
Hundred and Sixteen pounds</p>
<p><persName>Elias Bates</persName></p>
<p>1616 lbs   <placeName>Hereulaneum </placeName><date when="1817-08-26">26th Aug 1817</date></p>

<p><persName>Mr S F Austin</persName></p>
<p><persName>Mr John Staples</persName> Deliverd 67 Bars of lead weighing 2763lb</p>
<p><persName>Elias Bates</persName>    [Rubric]</p>
<p><placeName>Hereulaneum </placeName><date when="1817-08-28">28th Augt&#8212;1817</date></p>

<p><placeName>Hereulaneum </placeName><date when="1817-09-05">Sept 5th 1817</date></p>
<p>Received of <persName>John Staples</persName> or <persName>Bareer </persName>67 Bars of Lead weighing
twenty seven hundred and sixty six pounds for <persName>Stephen F. Austin</persName></p>
<p><persName>James Bates</persName>
for <persName>Elias Bates</persName></p>
<p>67 Bars 2766lbs</p>

<p><persName>Mr S F Austin</persName></p>
<p><persName>Mr John Staples</persName> Delivd 50 Bars of Lead weighing Two Thousand
and Thirteen pounds</p>
<p><persName>Ellas Bates</persName>    [Rubric]</p>
<p>50 Br 2013 lb    <date when="1817-09-20">Septr 20th 1817</date></p>

        </div1>
